\noindent Symbols of wrong class (ord):
\[ a \neg b           \qquad  x \square           y + z \]
Manual correction:
\[ a \mathbin{\neg} b \qquad  x \mathrel{\square} y + z \]
Symbols of correct class:
\[ a \bneg          b \qquad  x \rsquare          y + z \]
